data.description: XA. Country charmer in the heart of Ryderwood. This home has been updated with designer touches. Entertain or relax on the covered deck with built-in seating or on the floral patio. Plant your own garden in the fenced planter box area. Park two cars in the carport. Enjoy creating projects in the large garage with workshop attached.
